"  Crust:","1 1/2 cups all-purpose flour","1/4 teaspoon salt","4 tablespoons cold unsalted butter, cut into pieces","1/4 cup vegetable shortening, chilled","  FILLING:","6 ounces cream cheese, at room temperature","3/4 cup confectioners' sugar","1 1/2 cups heavy cream","1/2 teaspoon vanilla extract","2 cups strawberries, hulled and cut into quarters (8 oz.)","1  (6 oz.) basket raspberries","1  (4.4 oz.) basket blueberries"